                    <td class="val-new">$(printf "%'d" $N50_VAL) bp</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #7f8c8d; margin-top: 10px;">
            * Short-read polishing (if provided) resulted in a net change of <b>$(printf "%'d" $POS_CHANGED) bp</b>.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2 style="margin-top:0;">AMR Color Legend</h2>
        <div class="legend-container">
            <div class="legend-item"><div class="swatch" style="background:#3498db;"></div>Beta-lactams / Penicillins</div>
